    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I agree with most of @reaperrr's comment. Explosions and other sound effects have no place in `notifications.yaml`, and our TS mod should not contain any FS assets.\nThat being said, I don't agree with the last part - not \"registering\" assets in mod YAMLs has lead to enough headaches in TD, RA and D2k. We should have everything available for when we need it, not make people have to go through the mix files searching for the 1 sound they need every time they need something new.\nAll TS voice notifications should be added here. Nothing more, nothing less. Splitting into separate YAML files might be good, so once we see how many all notifications are we can discuss that.\n"
